data.title: MEDIA ADVISORY: jeremy messersmith to play a free online concert on International Workers’ Day tomorrow night
data.meta_description: Organized by grassroots organizations TakeAction Minnesota and the 100% Campaign
data.text:
Contact: Kenza Hadj-Moussa, 612-386-9556

MEDIA ADVISORY

jeremy messersmith to play a free online concert on International Workers’ Day tomorrow night

Organized by grassroots organizations TakeAction Minnesota and the 100% Campaign

WHEN: International Workers’ Day Friday, May 1 from 7:00 – 8:00 p.m. (TOMORROW)

WHAT: Free Quarantina livestream concert

WHERE: jeremy messersmith’s Instagram

WHO: TakeAction Minnesota, the 100% Campaign, and indie pop singer/songwriter jeremy messersmith, one of Minnesota’s most recognized and celebrated artists

More details: RSVP and get reminded. Family-friendly.

###

TakeAction Minnesota is a statewide, independent, multiracial people’s organization working to advance democracy and equity through organizing, political action, and campaigns. Offices are located in St. Paul, St. Cloud, and Duluth.www.takeactionminnesota.org

The 100% Campaign is bringing Minnesotans together – people who believe we need an equitable, clean energy future for everyone in our state.
